    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>一般颜色是由ARGB构成，在程序中可以用8位十六进制值表示，前2位表示A（透明度），后6位表示RGB（颜色）。</p><h3 id="透明度"><a href="#透明度" class="headerlink" title="透明度"></a>透明度</h3><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">StringBuilder str = <span class="keyword">new</span> StringBuilder();</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;= <span class="number">100</span>; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> round = Math.round(<span class="number">255</span> * i * <span class="number">1.0f</span> / <span class="number">100f</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    String hexString = Integer.toHexString(round);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (hexString.length() &lt; <span class="number">2</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        hexString += <span class="string">"0"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    str.append(<span class="string">"|"</span> + i + <span class="string">"%|"</span> + hexString.toUpperCase());</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(i % <span class="number">2</span> == <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        str.append(<span class="string">"|"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(str.toString());</span><br><span class="line">        str.delete(<span class="number">0</span>, str.length());</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><p>对照表： </p><table><thead><tr><th style="text-align:left">透明度</th><th style="text-align:center">16进制</th><th style="text-align:right">透明度</th><th style="text-align:right">16进制</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:left">全透</td><td style="text-align:center">00</td><td style="text-align:right">不透</td><td style="text-align:right">FF</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">1%</td><td style="text-align:center">30</td><td style="text-align:right">2%</td><td style="text-align:right">50</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">3%</td><td style="text-align:center">80</td><td style="text-align:right">4%</td><td style="text-align:right">A0</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">5%</td><td style="text-align:center">D0</td><td style="text-align:right">6%</td><td style="text-align:right">F0</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">7%</td><td style="text-align:center">12</td><td style="text-align:right">8%</td><td style="text-align:right">14</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">9%</td><td style="text-align:center">17</td><td style="text-align:right">10%</td><td style="text-align:right">1A</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">11%</td><td style="text-align:center">1C</td><td style="text-align:right">12%</td><td style="text-align:right">1F</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">13%</td><td style="text-align:center">21</td><td style="text-align:right">14%</td><td style="text-align:right">24</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">15%</td><td style="text-align:center">26</td><td style="text-align:right">16%</td><td style="text-align:right">29</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">17%</td><td style="text-align:center">2B</td><td style="text-align:right">18%</td><td style="text-align:right">2E</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">19%</td><td style="text-align:center">30</td><td style="tex